The '''brown-breasted barbet''' ('''''Pogonornis melanopterus''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Lybiidae]].
It is found in [[Kenya]], [[Malawi]], [[Mozambique]], [[Somalia]], and [[Tanzania]].





